data.description: Welcome to this charming two-story, 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home nestled in West Kyle. This beautifully designed residence offers spacious and comfortable living for the whole family. As you enter, you'll be greeted by a warm foyer and dining/office area inviting you into  a living area that flows seamlessly, creating an ideal setting for gatherings and relaxation.  The well-appointed kitchen boasts ample counter space and an adjacent breakfast nook bathed in natural light. A convenient half bath on the main floor adds to the practicality of the layout.  Upstairs, you'll discover a peaceful retreat with four thoughtfully designed bedrooms, providing both privacy and comfort. The primary bedroom features an en-suite bath, creating a tranquil oasis for rejuvenation. The remaining bedrooms share a well-appointed full bath, ensuring convenience for all family members and guests.  Outside, the home is surrounded by a meticulously landscaped yard, perfect for outdoor activities and entertaining. The vibrant community of Kyle offers a blend of suburban tranquility and easy access to urban amenities, making this residence an ideal place to call home. With its spacious interior, modern conveniences, and desirable location, this 4-bedroom gem in Kyle truly offers the best of both worlds.
